ESLint can enforce testing-related rules (e.g., no-focused-tests) or restrict use of flaky patterns, especially in test automation frameworks.

Integrates Well with CI/CD
You can include lint checks in your CI pipeline to automatically reject poorly formatted PRs, just like in real teams.